#: weblate_web/templates/about.html:168
msgid ""
"Michal is a libre software enthusiast born and residing in Prague, Czech "
"Republic. He is a long term contributor to various libre software projects "
"like <a href=\"https://weblate.org/\">Weblate</a>, <a href=\"https://"
"wammu.eu/\">Gammu</a>, <a href=\"https://www.phpmyadmin.net/\">phpMyAdmin</"
"a> and <a href=\"https://www.debian.org/\">Debian</a>."
msgstr ""
"Michal ເປັນຜູ້ມັກຊອບແວ libre ທີ່ເກີດ ແລະ ອາໄສຢູ່ໃນເມືອງ Prague, ສາທາລະນະລັດເຊັກ. "
"ລາວເປັນຜູ້ປະກອບສ່ວນໄລຍະຍາວໃຫ້ກັບໂປຣເຈັກຊອບແວ libre ຫຼາຍຢ່າງ ເຊັ່ນ: <a href=\"https://"
"weblate.org/\">Weblate</a>, <a href=\"https://wammu.eu/\">Gammu</a>, <a "
"href=\"https://www.phpmyadmin.net/\">phpMyAdmin</a> ແລະ <a href=\"https://"
"www.debian.org/\">Debian</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/about.html:171
msgid ""
"After employment in several technology companies, since early 2016, Michal "
"dedicated himself to providing services to companies focusing on "
"localization and Weblate."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັງຈາກການເຮັດວຽກໃນບໍລິສັດເທັກໂນໂລຊີຫຼາຍແຫ່ງ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ຕົ້ນປີ 2016, Michal "
"ໄດ້ອຸທິດຕົນເອງເພື່ອໃຫ້ບໍລິການແກ່ບໍລິສັດທີ່ເນັ້ນການແປພາສາ ແລະ Weblate."

