#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:14
msgid "Want to get a t-shirt or hoodie at our FOSDEM stand?"
msgstr "ຢາກໄດ້ເສື້ອຢືດ ຫຼື ເສື້ອກັນໜາວຢູ່ບູດ FOSDEM ຂອງພວກເຮົາບໍ່?"

