#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:21
msgid "Become a Weblate supporter"
msgstr "ມາເປັນຜູ້ສະໜັບສະໜູນ Weblate"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:28
msgid ""
"Weblate does not require payment, and welcomes donations. There are many "
"ways to contribute. Discuss it with your associates."
msgstr ""
"Weblate ບໍ່ຮຽກຮ້ອງການຊຳລະເງິນ ແລະ ຍິນດີຮັບການບໍລິຈາກ. ມີຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການປະກອບສ່ວນ. "
"ປຶກສາຫາລືກັບເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານຂອງເຈົ້າ."

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:32 weblate_web/templates/donate.html:79
msgid "Purchase premium cloud"
msgstr "ຊື້ພຣີມຽມຄລາວ"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:33
msgid "Manage your donations"
msgstr "ຈັດການການບໍລິຈາກຂອງເຈົ້າ"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:36
msgid "Recurring support and rewards"
msgstr "ການສະໜັບສະໜູນແບບຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ ແລະ ລາງວັນ"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:39
msgid ""
"Recurring donations facilitate sustainable Weblate development, and even the "
"smallest amount is put to good use. Repeated appreciation helps in keeping "
"the project sustainable long term. Please consider this option if you are "
"hosting Weblate yourself without a support contract."
msgstr ""
"ການບໍລິຈາກແບບຕໍ່ເນື່ອງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການພັດທະນາ Weblate ຍືນຍົງ, ແລະ "
"ເຖິງແມ່ນຈຳນວນເງິນນ້ອຍໆກໍຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃຫ້ເກີດປະໂຫຍດ. "
"ການສະແດງຄວາມຂອບໃຈຊ້ຳໆຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ໂຄງການຍືນຍົງໃນໄລຍະຍາວ. ກະລຸນາພິຈາລະນາທາງເລືອກນີ້ ຖ້າເຈົ້າໂຮສ "
"Weblate ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໂດຍບໍ່ມີສັນຍາສະໜັບສະໜູນ."

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:41
msgid "Choose your reward"
msgstr "ເລືອກລາງວັນຂອງເຈົ້າ"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:47 weblate_web/templates/donate.html:54
#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:61 weblate_web/templates/support.html:82
#: weblate_web/templates/support.html:99 weblate_web/templates/support.html:117
#: weblate_web/templates/support.html:153
msgid "annually"
msgstr "ຕໍ່ປີ"

#: weblate_web/templates/donate.html:48 weblate_web/templates/donate.html:55
